{"tid":601392,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"科索沃國會勇武抗爭，反對黨掟催淚彈阻投票","createTime":"2018-03-22T07:44:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T08:38:15.000Z","uid":54344,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"201303418ecfa37e75f6371cb79720277bd0e2c3","tid":601392,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T07:44:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cnn.com/2018/03/21/europe/kosovo-parliament-tear-gas-intl/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2018%2F03%2F21%2Feurope%2Fkosovo-parliament-tear-gas-intl%2Findex.html&d=MsmEIM2wZNZ637CA7cgqp9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=2714cc2d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2018%2F03%2F21%2Feurope%2Fkosovo-parliament-tear-gas-intl%2Findex.html&h=38ec3d91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnn.com/2018/03/21/europe/kosovo-parliament-tear-gas-intl/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180322/57978524\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180322%2F57978524&d=MsmEIM2wZNZ637CA7cgqp9r9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=cddb104c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180322%2F57978524&h=55188fa4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180322/57978524</a><br />\n<br />\n科索沃國會周三原定就與鄰國黑山的邊界協議進行投票，有反對派議員不滿協議使國家領土縮小，在議事廳內投擲三枚催淚彈抗議，議員在一片煙霧瀰漫下狼狽撤走。<br />\n<br />\n科索沃國會由120人組成，原預料可以超過2/3贊成票通過邊界協議，但自決行動黨 （Self-Determination Movement Party）指，協議錯誤地割讓2萬英畝屬於科索沃的領土，於是投擲催淚彈阻止投票。網上片段顯示，議事廳內被大量煙霧籠罩，議員們掩着口鼻離開。該黨過去曾用過相同招數阻止投票，五名涉事議員事後被捕。<br />\n根據歐盟要求，科索沃必須通過這份邊界協議，公民才可享免簽證進入申根區待遇，黑山早前已通過協議。科索沃議長韋塞利（Kadri Veseli）表示：「我們不會向暴力及民粹低頭，通過協議將鞏固我們的主權，解放我們通往歐洲融合之路。」他揚言要如期通過協議。歐盟及美國駐科索沃大使分別譴責暴力行為，呼籲議員回到議事廳完成投票。<br />\n<br />\n望下販民？叫下結束一黨專政都唔撚敢 真係好撚失望 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23673deadc4910599357c0f682ac8365cad94e4b","tid":601392,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T07:54:25.000Z","msg":"我記得之前玩完話要買金屬機就防止帶入去<br />\n點解今日又可以玩多次"},{"pid":"92280e6db2b8fb517e7ab654d6d66ad521517a1c","tid":601392,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23673deadc4910599357c0f682ac8365cad94e4b","tid":601392,"uid":3241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T07:54:25.000Z","msg":"我記得之前玩完話要買金屬機就防止帶入去<br />\n點解今日又可以玩多次"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T08:01:56.000Z","msg":"睇CNN冇講話之前掟過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔睇蘋果都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e718c86474764d6453c000b44f0610089c9fe3e","tid":601392,"uid":166054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T08:38:15.000Z","msg":"點解人地咁易就可以帶催淚彈入議會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}